data.title: DVD Japanese Music Shop New
data.meta_description:
DVD Japanese Music Shop New - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides information about purchasing Japanese music DVDs and discographies from an online shop, including:
- Contact details and payment/shipping information for the shop
- Price lists for DVDs, MP4/AVI files, and discographies of various Japanese artists
- Lists of albums included in the discography purchase for over 100 listed artists ranging from 1212 to cali
